{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/psychosis-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/psychosis-and-driving","title":"Psychosis and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:19:44+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2340","business_proposition":false,"description":"You must tell DVLA if you suffer from psychosis","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you suffer from psychosis.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorbike licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in the &lsquo;M1 questionnaire&rsquo; and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_066650.pdf\" title=\"Download ‘M1 medical fitness to drive questionnaire’ (PDF, 252KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘M1 medical fitness to drive questionnaire’ (PDF, 252KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in the &lsquo;M1V questionnaire&rsquo; and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_172725.pdf\" title=\"Download ‘M1V medical fitness to drive questionnaire’ (PDF, 243KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘M1V medical fitness to drive questionnaire’ (PDF, 243KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:25:08+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-08T10:36:08+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:45:33+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-30T12:27:11+00:00"}]}